<h2>Sasolburg Baptist Church</h2>
<h5>Advancing the Kingdom <em>Matthew 11:12</em></h5>

<p>The <a href="pics.html">Sasolburg Baptist Church</a> is a member of the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Baptist_Union_of_Southern_Africa">Baptist Union of Southern Africa</a>. The Church acknowledges Jesus Christ as the Supreme Head of the Church, and undertakes to manage all its affairs according to the New Testament teaching and recognises the sole authority of the Holy Scriptures in all matters of faith and conduct.</p>

